---
---

<section id="changelog" class="security-section alt final" data-security-section>
  <div class="security-container-narrow">
    <div class="change-head">
      <div class="bb-eyebrow">Security changelog</div>
      <h2 class="bb-display-l">What changed, when, and why.</h2>
      <p>
        We log every security-relevant change here: cryptographic primitive upgrades,
        key-rotation events, post-mortems, and resolved disclosures.
      </p>
    </div>

    <article class="empty-change">
      <div class="clock">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Nothing to report yet.</h3>
      <p>
        When entries appear here, they will list the change, the date, the
        affected components, and the reasoning. This page exists so that
        changes are public, dated, and auditable.
      </p>
    </article>

    <p class="rss">
      Subscribe via RSS at <span>beebeeb.io/security.rss</span> — coming soon.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .change-head {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .change-head .bb-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .change-head h2 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 42px);
  }

  .change-head p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .empty-change {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--paper);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .clock {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px dashed var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--paper-2);
    color: var(--ink-3);
  }

  .clock svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
  }

  .empty-change h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .empty-change p {
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .rss {
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .rss span {
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
</style>
